        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer755567306" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6552767953116315729">Terrific. The main concept is that although moral questions are often very difficult to answer, and there are usually many satisfactory answers to each one, we can use the principles of science to eliminate the obviously bad answers to those questions.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


